        {
            "title": "歐洲央行7月會議紀要顯示 官員認為通膨風險「總體平衡」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐洲央行7月會議紀要顯示，多數官員認為通膨風險「總體平衡」，他們對於消費價格的展望仍然適用。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周四公佈的會議摘要顯示，儘管提及進一步降息，但在已八次降息後將存款利率維持在2%被視為「穩健」做法。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">會議紀要稱，「多數成員認為通膨前景面臨的風險總體平衡。會議指出，近期歐元區經濟數據展現的韌性已在6月預測基準情境中充分體現，且該預測已獲得廣泛驗證。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場普遍預期歐洲央行將在不到兩周後第二次維持借貸成本不變。經濟學家預測12月將再次降息，但投資者已不再充分消化進一步降息的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">多數決策者認為當前利率水平合理，通膨率維持在2%目標附近，經濟迄今對關稅、戰爭等逆風因素展現出韌性。7月，歐盟與美國達成貿易協議，為該地區多數出口商品鎖定15%的關稅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題ECB Officials Saw Inflation Risks as ‘Broadly Balanced’ in July</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C7%E6%9C%88%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E7%B4%80%E8%A6%81%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA-%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-%E7%B8%BD%E9%AB%94%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1-133949423.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 01:15:42",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "楊受成破天荒拍賣藏酒　426瓶「酒王」估值超過呢個數｜財經熱話",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"楊受成首次拍賣美酒，426瓶瓶珍酩估值逾千萬。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Qv8TDFg.7XiOEPZU405p0Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/sl/am730_578/f98a5f0f1e7b2925e2efc216e7a3b241\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">楊受成首次拍賣美酒，426瓶瓶珍酩估值逾千萬。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>英皇國際(163)主席<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:楊受成;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/楊受成\">楊受成</a>首次推出私人美酒窖藏拍賣。據香港蘇富比資料，「楊受成博士至尊窖藏珍酩」拍賣會將於9月10日下午3時舉行。今次拍賣</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>匯集楊受成窖藏中426瓶「至尊窖藏珍酩」，總估值高達逾千萬港元</span></span></span></span></span>，引發關注。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">涵蓋羅曼尼康帝等  「無一不是傳世經典」</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>根據</span><span>蘇富比網頁介紹，楊受成此次拍賣的美酒</span></span></span></span></span>涵蓋多款傳世名釀，<span><span><span><span><span>除了羅曼尼康帝(Romanée Conti)特級園系列外，還有Henri Jayer、Leroy、Coche-Dury、柏翠堡等名莊的珍釀，強調「其集中程度遠遠超越世界上任何倉存」。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>蘇富比洋酒部亞洲區主管更寫道，當</span></span></span></span></span>踏入<span><span><span><span><span>楊受成</span></span></span></span></span>酒窖時「為之震撼，<span><span><span><span><span>映入眼簾的皆是頂級瑰釀，整齊陳列着洋酒界中最偉大的名字」，並</span></span></span></span></span>讚譽「此處所藏，無一不是傳世經典。」</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">此前英皇傳出166億債務危機</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span>此前，英皇國際傳出債務危機，</span></span></span><span><span><span>6</span></span></span><span><span><span>月份公告顯示截至3月底逾期貸款達166億港元，<span><span>遭核數師「不發表意見」，其後傳出向債權人提交債務重組方案，尋求延長銀行貸款期限，惹來輿論關注。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/楊受成破天荒拍賣藏酒-426瓶-酒王-估值超過呢個數-財經熱話/593759?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/楊受成破天荒拍賣藏酒-426瓶-酒王-估值超過呢個數-財經熱話/593759?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/楊受成破天荒拍賣藏酒-426瓶-酒王-估值超過呢個數-財經熱話/593759?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A5%8A%E5%8F%97%E6%88%90%E7%A0%B4%E5%A4%A9%E8%8D%92%E6%8B%8D%E8%B3%A3%E8%97%8F%E9%85%92-426%E7%93%B6-%E9%85%92%E7%8E%8B-%E4%BC%B0%E5%80%BC%E8%B6%85%E9%81%8E%E5%91%A2%E5%80%8B%E6%95%B8-%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-091500863.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-28 17:35:47",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國第二季度經濟增速修正至3.3% 受投資改善推動",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 第二季度美國經濟成長速度略快於初值水平，這得益於企業投資回升和貿易的強勁推動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國經濟分析局周四公佈的修正數據顯示，經通膨調整後的國內生產毛額（衡量美國生產的商品和服務價值）折合年率成長3.3%。初值報告的增速為3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">淨出口為GDP貢獻近5個百分點，創紀錄最高水平；此前淨出口在今年前三個月拖累了GDP成長。非美國產的商品和服務在GDP計算中會被扣除，但在消費發生時會被計入。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Economy Expands at Revised 3.3% Rate as Investment Improved</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Augusta Saraiva、Matthew Boesler、Molly Smith.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%9F%E4%BF%AE%E6%AD%A3%E8%87%B33-3-%E5%8F%97%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95-125152427.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-28 22:50:47",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國上周首次申領失業金人數小幅下降至22.9萬人",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 上周美國首次申領失業救濟人數小幅下降，表明在經濟前景不確定的情況下雇主仍儘量保留現有員工。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在截至8月23日當周，首次申領失業救濟人數減少了5,000人，降至22.9萬人。彭博對經濟學家的調查得到的預測中值為23萬人。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據勞工部周四公佈的數據，持續申領失業救濟人數在之前一周也下降至195萬人。那一周正是美國政府月度就業報告的調查期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">到目前為止，企業雖不願大規模裁員，但已減少招聘。與此同時，持續申領失業救濟金人數居高不下，表明失業者找到新工作的時間在延長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">就業市場降溫的跡象已成為聯儲會官員關注的焦點。在上周於傑克遜霍爾舉行的聯儲會年度會議上，主席傑羅姆·鮑威爾在講話中表示「就業面臨的下行風險正在上升」，並為降息打開了大門。投資者由此預計，聯儲會將在下個月的政策會議上降息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">首次申領失業金的的四周移動均值上升至22.85萬人。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">未進行季節性調整的基礎上，上周首次申領失業金人數下降，其中愛荷華州降幅最大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Initial Jobless Claims Edged Down to 229,000 Last Week</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(增加第三段之後的內容)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8A%E5%91%A8%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E7%94%B3%E9%A0%98%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E9%87%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%85%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D%E8%87%B322-9%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA-124906812.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-28 22:50:49",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "看圖論市：南向資金淨賣出港股逾200億港元 創歷史最大",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zejrveX9zsM0ZzkG7rSHLg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3cf578c29cfe1a7a5cd38f5e2446235b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oppV95wp2MF6Zio88fUC_A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/78057f42050bfb73bf5e9bacd4769e40\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 周四A股和港股再度呈現強弱分化走勢，內地南向資金在港股走弱之際大額淨賣出。彭博數據顯示，今日南向資金淨賣出港股逾204億港元，為紀錄最大單日淨賣出。恒生指數午後收窄部分跌幅，但收盤仍跌0.8%，而上證綜指則收升逾1.1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9C%8B%E5%9C%96%E8%AB%96%E5%B8%82-%E5%8D%97%E5%90%91%E8%B3%87%E9%87%91%E6%B7%A8%E8%B3%A3%E5%87%BA%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E9%80%BE200%E5%84%84%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83-%E5%89%B5%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7-081750016.html",
